      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><ul><li><p>Set SOP Path parameter on the SOP Import LOP.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a4da7339-8264-4811-b1f3-5e7d5cd9ed90\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>RenderMan only supports imported OpenVDB (VDB) volume SOPs. You must export the VDB simulation prior to rendering.</p></div></div></li></ul><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"566\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_sopimport.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081388&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=566&amp;height=382\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640830/rfh_solaris_sopimport.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081388&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"382\" data-width=\"566\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640847\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_solaris_sopimport.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640830\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"19947ce1-97b8-4c54-850b-8b6618961d96\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_sopimport.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081388&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=566&amp;height=382 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_sopimport.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081388&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=566&amp;height=382 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Create volume material network inside the Material Library LOP using <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661555\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrVolume</a>. The network below is an example network for rendering a fireball using the density, temperature, and heat grids</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"dc3c312e-1680-4379-ad38-1f2eda4cabf4\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Currently only float grids can be rendered. Volume motion blur is not yet supported since RenderMan requires velocity to be a single vector grid rather than 3 float grids.</p></div></div></li></ul><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"803\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_pxrvolume.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=803&amp;height=357\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640830/rfh_solaris_pxrvolume.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"357\" data-width=\"803\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640844\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_solaris_pxrvolume.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640830\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bb4c3e01-7187-4222-838d-1f8710ad5ab2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_pxrvolume.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=803&amp;height=357 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640830/rfh_solaris_pxrvolume.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433081387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=803&amp;height=357 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Assign Material as usual using the path</p></li></ul><p />"
